# MySmartHop тАФ PRD, Architecture & Development Plan

## 1. Product Overview

**MySmartHop** is an AI-powered ride-sharing platform for a hackathon demo. It features two user roles (Public rider priority, Driver secondary), ML-based ride clustering, dynamic fare prediction, and intelligent driver ranking тАФ all backed by Supabase realtime infrastructure.

### 1.1 Problem Statement
Traditional ride-hailing apps treat every ride as isolated. MySmartHop groups nearby riders heading in similar directions, predicts optimized fares, and ranks drivers intelligently тАФ reducing cost and wait time.

### 1.2 Success Metrics (Hackathon)
- Working end-to-end ride flow (request тЖТ accept тЖТ complete тЖТ rate)
- ML models visibly influencing the product (clustering, fares, driver ranking)
- Realtime updates between rider and driver
- Clean, modern UI that impresses judges

