## 2. User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Supabase Project**: You need a Supabase project. Do you already have one, or should we set one up during Phase 1? I need the project URL and anon key.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Map Provider**: The plan uses **Leaflet.js with OpenStreetMap** (completely free, no API key needed) instead of Google Maps/Mapbox. This is ideal for a hackathon тАФ zero cost, fast setup, and looks professional. Do you agree, or do you prefer Mapbox/Google Maps?

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **ML Service Strategy**: For a hackathon, I recommend embedding the ML models **directly as Next.js API routes** using a lightweight Python subprocess or pre-computed results stored in Supabase тАФ instead of a separate FastAPI service. This eliminates deployment complexity. If you want the full FastAPI setup for demonstration/architecture points, we can keep it. What's your preference?

> [!WARNING]
> **TailwindCSS Version**: You requested TailwindCSS. I'll use **TailwindCSS v4** (latest) with shadcn/ui. Confirm this works for you.

