## 3. Finalized Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology | Reason |
|---|---|---|
| **Framework** | Next.js 15 (App Router) | SSR, API routes, modern React |
| **Language** | TypeScript | Type safety, better DX |
| **Styling** | TailwindCSS v4 + shadcn/ui | Rapid, beautiful components |
| **Animations** | Framer Motion | Smooth, professional transitions |
| **Database** | Supabase (PostgreSQL + PostGIS) | Auth, DB, Realtime in one |
| **Auth** | Supabase Auth (Email/OTP) | Built-in, role-based |
| **Realtime** | Supabase Realtime | WebSocket ride status updates |
| **Maps** | Leaflet.js + OpenStreetMap | Free, no API key, great UX |
| **ML Service** | FastAPI (Python) | Model serving endpoints |
| **ML Libraries** | scikit-learn, pandas, numpy | Clustering, regression, ranking |
| **Model Persistence** | joblib | Save/load trained models |
| **Charts** | Recharts | ML metrics visualization |

