## 4. System Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph Frontend["Next.js Frontend"]
        LP[Landing Page]
        AUTH[Auth Pages]
        PD[Public Dashboard]
        DD[Driver Dashboard]
        RS[Ride Status Page]
        AN[Analytics Dashboard]
    end

    subgraph Backend["Next.js API Routes"]
        AR[Auth Routes]
        RR[Ride Routes]
        DR[Driver Routes]
        MLR[ML Proxy Routes]
    end

    subgraph ML["FastAPI ML Service"]
        CL["/cluster тАФ KMeans/DBSCAN"]
        FP["/predict-fare тАФ Regression"]
        RD["/rank-driver тАФ Scoring"]
    end

    subgraph Supabase["Supabase"]
        SB_AUTH[Supabase Auth]
        SB_DB[(PostgreSQL + PostGIS)]
        SB_RT[Realtime Subscriptions]
    end

    Frontend -->|API Calls| Backend
    Backend -->|Auth| SB_AUTH
    Backend -->|CRUD| SB_DB
    Backend -->|ML Inference| ML
    ML -->|Store Results| SB_DB
    SB_RT -->|WebSocket| Frontend
    SB_DB -->|Triggers| SB_RT
```

